                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8343" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2093</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2382 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矢志不移：后疫情时代下海底捞的扩张之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Unwavering determination: Haidilao’s expansion path in the post pandemic era</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胡建雄，吴艺文，葛佳慧，曹頔，马浩宇，张雨婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海底捞餐饮股份责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海底捞；扩张战略；战略调整</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Haidilao；Expansion Strategy；Strategic Adjustment</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海底捞是餐饮行业的龙头企业，从地方小作坊起家并逐步扩张到成功上市，在行业激烈竞争的压力下探索持续发展的扩张战略，即便遭遇了打击也能迅速应对，最终成为餐饮业的标杆。2020年，外部疫情席卷，内部管理失衡等重重问题隐患，导致海底捞利润一路下滑。面对困境，后疫情时代下海底捞积极自救，采取一系列调整措施进行应对，并坚持扩张战略。最终海底捞走出业绩亏损的阴霾，并提交了一份亮眼的答卷。具体而言，尽管付出高昂代价，但是海底捞经过“啄木鸟计划”“硬骨头计划”等调整，着力实施多元化、密集型扩张战略，助推业绩再创新高。仅2023年上半年营业收入就达到188.9亿元，比2022年同期增长24.6%，实现净利润22.6亿，几乎与2019年全年实现的净利润持平。本案例以海底捞矢志不移的扩张之路为主线，描述海底捞扩张战略的发展历程，突出了海底捞扩张面临的问题、以及后续的战略调整措施，反映后疫情时代下海底捞继续扩张的战略规划，同时对餐饮行业的扩张战略提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Haidilao is a leading enterprise in the catering industry, starting from local small workshops and gradually expanding to successfully go public. Under the pressure of fierce competition in the industry, it explores a sustainable expansion strategy and can quickly respond even in the face of setbacks, ultimately becoming a benchmark in the catering industry. In 2020, the external epidemic swept through and internal management imbalances and other hidden problems led to a continuous decline in Haidilao’s profits. Faced with difficulties, in the post pandemic era, Hai Di Lao actively rescued itself and took a series of adjustment measures to respond, and adheres to an expansion strategy. In the end, Hai Di Lao emerged from the haze of performance losses and submitted a brilliant answer sheet. Specifically, despite paying a high price, Hai Di Lao has undergone adjustments such as the “Woodpecker Plan” and “Hardbone Plan” to focus on implementing a diversified and intensive expansion strategy, helping to push its performance to new highs. In the first half of 2023 alone, the operating revenue reached 18.89 billion yuan, an increase of 24.6% compared to the same period in 2022, achieving a net profit of 2.26 billion yuan, almost equal to the net profit achieved throughout 2019. This case takes Haidilao’s unwavering expansion path as the main line, describing the development process of Haidilao’s expansion strategy, highlighting the problems faced by Haidilao’s expansion in the post pandemic era, and the subsequent strategic adjustment measures, reflecting Haidilao’s strategic planning for continued expansion in the post pandemic era, and providing reference for the expansion strategy of the catering industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司战略与风险管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">扩张战略概念、类型；扩张战略动因；扩张战略实现条件；扩张战略调整</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-05</td>
                            </tr>
